Sean: I'M PROUD OF THE BUSINESS

02:56.410 --> 02:59.436
WE STARTED FROM NOTHING.

02:59.440 --> 03:01.635
WE'RE SELF-MADE MEN.

03:01.640 --> 03:02.504
