THE ONLY REASON I PASSED WAS

03:17.760 --> 03:19.523
BECAUSE YOU TUTORED ME AND

03:19.530 --> 03:20.622
WOULDN'T GIVE UP UNTIL I'D

03:20.630 --> 03:21.790
LEARNED IT.

