BUT I NEVER BECAME IT.

03:24.570 --> 03:26.367
I'M A MIMIC.

03:26.370 --> 03:28.292
I'M A MYNA BIRD WITH A SCALPEL.

03:28.300 --> 03:30.461
NO, NO, WORSE.

03:30.470 --> 03:33.928
I'M BOBOLIT IN BETTER SUITS.

03:33.940 --> 03:35.805
I DON'T EXCEL AT ANYTHING--

03:35.810 --> 03:38.699
RELATIONSHIPS, MY PROFESSION.

03:38.710 --> 03:40.712
ALL I HAVE TO OFFER IS A GREAT

03:40.720 --> 03:42.915
SMILE AND A CONVINCING LINE OF

03:42.920 --> 03:43.909
BULLSHIT.

