IT'S A STATISTICAL METHOD THAT

04:46.480 --> 04:47.811
PROVIDES A MEASURE OF SURVIVAL

04:47.820 --> 04:49.481
TIME WEIGHTED BY A PATIENT'S

04:49.490 --> 04:51.082
QUALITY OF LIFE.

04:51.090 --> 04:52.785
QUALITY TIME WITHOUT SYMPTOMS

04:52.790 --> 04:55.054
AND TOXICITY--Q-TWIST.

04:55.060 --> 04:56.755
Megan: THAT'S VERY CLEVER.

04:56.760 --> 04:58.022
Doctor: AND USEFUL.

04:58.030 --> 05:00.055
IT'S HOW WE DETERMINE IF

05:00.060 --> 05:00.924
AN ALTERNATIVE COURSE OF

05:00.930 --> 05:02.022
TREATMENT IS WARRANTED.

