Sean: IF? THERE'S NO IF UNLESS

05:03.530 --> 05:04.895
IT'S FOLLOWED BY A THEN.

05:04.900 --> 05:06.390
IF TAMOXOPHEN DOESN'T WORK,

05:06.400 --> 05:07.731
THEN WE TRY SOMETHING ELSE--

05:07.740 --> 05:08.934
EXPERIMENTAL TRIALS, CLINICAL

05:08.940 --> 05:09.861
TRIALS.

05:09.870 --> 05:10.632
I'M A DOCTOR.

05:10.640 --> 05:11.538
I'LL PULL WHATEVER STRINGS

05:11.540 --> 05:12.370
I NEED TO.

05:12.380 --> 05:13.005
Doctor: DR. McNAMARA, WHEN

05:13.010 --> 05:13.977
YOU COMPARE THE PATIENT'S

05:13.980 --> 05:15.834
OVERALL SURVIVAL WITH HIS OR

05:15.840 --> 05:17.546
HER CLINICAL HEALTH STATE--

05:17.550 --> 05:18.505
Sean: THE PATIENT'S NAME IS

05:18.510 --> 05:19.511
MEGAN.

05:19.520 --> 05:21.010
Doctor: YES, AND ACCORDING TO

05:21.020 --> 05:22.487
MEGAN'S Q-TWIST--

05:22.490 --> 05:23.639
Megan: SHE'D BE BETTER OFF DEAD.

05:26.820 --> 05:28.788
Doctor: MEGAN, THERE ARE ALWAYS

05:28.790 --> 05:31.429
WAYS OF FIGHTING.

05:31.430 --> 05:32.454
IT'S ENTIRELY UP TO YOU TO

05:32.460 --> 05:33.722
DECIDE WHETHER THE BENEFITS

05:33.730 --> 05:34.924
OUTWEIGH THE COSTS.

05:37.630 --> 05:38.528
Sean: COULD YOU GIVE US

05:38.530 --> 05:39.758
