41:06.290 --> 41:07.257
YOU WANT SOME?

41:07.260 --> 41:08.727
Sean: NO, THANKS.

41:08.730 --> 41:10.095
Julia: DO YOU WANT ME TO ORDER

41:10.100 --> 41:11.658
OUT?

41:11.670 --> 41:13.820
Sean: I'M NOT THAT HUNGRY.

41:13.830 --> 41:15.138
Julia: DID YOU HAVE AN AFFAIR

41:15.140 --> 41:18.701
WITH HER?

41:18.710 --> 41:21.031
Sean: YES.

41:33.920 --> 41:39.222
[SEAN SIGHS]

41:39.230 --> 41:44.827
Julia: PLEASE DON'T TOUCH ME.

41:44.830 --> 41:49.665
[JULIA SIGHS]

41:49.670 --> 41:51.706
WHEN DID IT START?

41:51.710 --> 41:53.962
Sean: AFTER YOU LOST THE BABY.

41:53.970 --> 41:55.176
RIGHT AROUND THE TIME YOU

41:55.180 --> 41:57.330
STARTED SLEEPING WITH JUDE.

41:57.340 --> 41:59.069
Julia: I DIDN'T SLEEP

41:59.080 --> 42:00.274
WITH JUDE, SEAN.

42:00.280 --> 42:01.304
Sean: JULIA, DON'T EMBARRASS

42:01.310 --> 42:02.914
YOURSELF WITH A LIE.

42:02.920 --> 42:04.171
Julia: LIKE YOU HAVE FOR MONTHS?

42:04.180 --> 42:07.115
Sean: I FOUND A PICTURE IN YOUR

42:07.120 --> 42:08.109
BOOK.

42:08.120 --> 42:09.348
Julia: YOU WENT THROUGH

42:09.360 --> 42:10.713
MY THINGS?

42:10.720 --> 42:11.755
Sean: YES. AND I FOUND

42:11.760 --> 42:12.988
THE HALF-NAKED PICTURE OF A BOY

42:12.990 --> 42:14.184
ONLY A FEW YEARS OLDER

42:14.190 --> 42:15.191
THAN YOUR SON.

42:15.200 --> 42:17.020
AND IN THAT SECOND, I HATED YOU

42:17.030 --> 42:20.067
FOR WHAT YOU'D DONE.

42:20.070 --> 42:22.959
AND I KNEW.

42:22.970 --> 42:24.961
AND I TURNED TO SOMEONE

42:24.970 --> 42:28.337
WHO COULD COMFORT ME.

42:28.340 --> 42:30.774
AND SHE DID.

42:30.780 --> 42:31.906
Julia: I DIDN'T SLEEP

42:31.910 --> 42:32.899
WITH HIM, SEAN.

42:32.910 --> 42:34.775
Sean: THAT'S NOT TRUE. I KNOW!

42:34.780 --> 42:36.247
Julia: WAS I TEMPTED?

42:36.250 --> 42:37.808
DID I WANT TO? YES, I DID,

42:37.820 --> 42:39.310
I'M ASHAMED TO SAY,

42:39.320 --> 42:43.654
BUT I ALWAYS WANTED YOU MORE,

42:43.660 --> 42:44.979
SO WHEN IT CAME TO IT,

42:44.990 --> 42:48.084
I DID NOTHING.

42:48.090 --> 42:52.698
[LAUGHS]

42:52.700 --> 43:00.800
[CRYING]

43:00.810 --> 43:08.103
Julia: DID YOU LOVE HER?

43:08.110 --> 43:09.816
Sean: YES.

43:09.820 --> 43:12.141
[JULIA SOBS]

43:12.150 --> 43:15.415
Julia: DO YOU LOVE ME ANYMORE?

43:15.420 --> 43:16.682
Sean: MORE THAN YOU'LL EVER

43:16.690 --> 43:18.180
KNOW.

43:18.190 --> 43:19.384
Julia: AND THIS IS HOW

43:19.390 --> 43:20.789
YOU SHOW IT, SEAN?

43:21.930 --> 43:24.057
PATIENCE AND MY FIDELITY AND

43:24.060 --> 43:26.392
THE SANCTITY OF OUR CHILDREN

43:26.400 --> 43:27.867
AND OUR MARRIAGE, BY SCREWING

43:27.870 --> 43:29.861
ANOTHER WOMAN?

43:29.870 --> 43:31.735
GOD! EVEN YOUR INFIDELITY

43:31.740 --> 43:34.709
IS PASSIVE-AGRESSIVE!

43:34.710 --> 43:36.371
Sean: HOW'S THAT?

43:36.380 --> 43:38.439
Julia: BECAUSE SHE'S DEAD, SEAN!

43:38.440 --> 43:40.044
SHE'S DEAD!

43:40.050 --> 43:42.109
AND SHE DIED A HORRIBLE DEATH,

43:42.120 --> 43:44.179
AND I CAN'T HATE A WOMAN WHO

43:44.180 --> 43:48.184
DIED OF CANCER AT 36.

43:48.190 --> 43:49.748
Sean: HIT ME.

43:49.760 --> 43:51.387
YOU WANT TO.

43:51.390 --> 43:52.322
DO IT.

43:52.330 --> 43:53.319
I DESERVE IT.

43:53.330 --> 43:54.729
THERE'S NOT A CUP HANDY.

43:54.730 --> 43:56.027
JUST HIT ME!

43:56.030 --> 43:57.725
Julia: I DON'T HAVE THE ENERGY

43:57.730 --> 43:59.721
TO HIT YOU, SEAN.

43:59.730 --> 44:01.891
OR TO HATE YOU...

44:01.900 --> 44:04.164
OR TO LOVE YOU ANYMORE.

44:04.170 --> 44:06.309
BUT YOU OWE ME THIS...

44:06.310 --> 44:10.030
IT'S ALL I WANT TO KNOW.

44:10.040 --> 44:11.849
WHAT DID SHE GIVE YOU

44:11.850 --> 44:16.219
THAT I COULDN'T?

44:16.220 --> 44:18.211
Sean: SHE SAW THE GOOD IN ME,

44:18.220 --> 44:20.415
JULIA.

44:20.420 --> 44:26.859
SHE SAW THE POTENTIAL, THE HOPE.

44:26.860 --> 44:29.294
EVERY TIME YOU LOOK AT ME,

44:29.300 --> 44:31.325
I SEE IT IN YOUR EYES.

44:31.330 --> 44:33.719
ALL I SEE STARING BACK AT ME

44:33.730 --> 44:36.767
IS REGRET.

44:36.770 --> 44:39.330
ISN'T THAT TRUE?

44:39.340 --> 44:40.807
Julia: YES.

44:40.810 --> 44:44.803
FOR BOTH OF US.

44:44.810 --> 44:48.200
[LAUGHS]

44:48.210 --> 44:51.816
WE WERE SO HAPPY, SEAN.

44:51.820 --> 44:55.153
WE COULD DO ANYTHING TOGETHER.

44:55.160 --> 44:57.048
[SNIFFLES]

44:57.060 --> 44:58.789
THE NIGHT WE GOT MARRIED,

44:58.790 --> 45:02.123
I...I COULDN'T SLEEP.

45:02.130 --> 45:05.759
ALL I DID WAS STARE AT YOU.

45:05.770 --> 45:09.092
I WAS SO IN LOVE WITH YOU.

45:09.100 --> 45:13.867
IT WAS SO FULL OF PROMISE.

45:13.870 --> 45:15.838
AND NOW IT'S ALL GONE,

45:15.840 --> 45:17.376
AND IT'S ALL TURNED TO ASH,

45:17.380 --> 45:21.043
JUST LIKE MEGAN.

45:21.050 --> 45:26.943
AND IT BREAKS MY HEART.

45:26.950 --> 45:28.815
Sean: I CAN'T LOSE YOU,

45:28.820 --> 45:31.015
TOO, JULIA.

45:31.020 --> 45:36.925
[JULIA SNIFFLES]

45:36.930 --> 45:38.557
Julia: WE LOST EACH OTHER

45:38.560 --> 45:41.996
A LONG TIME AGO, SEAN.

45:42.000 --> 45:43.934
[SEAN SOBBING]

45:52.550 --> 45:56.179
Sean: I'M SO SORRY.

45:56.180 --> 46:01.482
I'M SO SORRY.

46:01.490 --> 46:04.459
I'M SO SORRY.

46:04.460 --> 46:06.951
